short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Calculate prices quickly when buying tissue culture plants
short.vi: Tính giá nhanh khi mua các loại cây nuôi cấy mô

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The "Tissue Culture Plants for Sale" application on Chrome Extension is a tool to assist users in shopping and learning about ornamental plants based on tissue culture techniques. Here are the main features of the application:

Quick Pricing: Users can easily calculate product prices based on the quantity they want to buy. This helps them know the total value of their order before proceeding with payment.

Show detailed product information: The application provides detailed information about bonsai products using tissue culture techniques. The information includes the product name, description, price, shipping method and even available illustrations for each product. This helps users have a comprehensive view of ornamental plants and easily choose the right product for their needs.
